files.Title: ECS.Core.EventBus
files.Summary: The event bus, a central system for managing event publication and subscription. Any subscriber to the type will recieve the published event. Each handles an event of type .

files.Title: ECS.Systems.Collision.CollisionResponseSystem
files.Summary: Handles physical responses to collisions between entities using impulse-based resolution. Implements position correction and velocity response for realistic collision behavior.
